## Advanced Google Dorking Queries for LinkedIn Remote OSINT Positions

### General Remote OSINT Roles
```
site:linkedin.com ("OSINT" OR "Open Source Intelligence" OR "Open source analyst") AND ("we're hiring" OR "join our remote team" OR "remote position") AND ("remote" OR "work from home" OR "WFH")
```

### Remote OSINT Analyst Positions
```
site:linkedin.com ("OSINT analyst" OR "Open Source Analyst") AND ("remote hiring" OR "remote positions available") AND ("remote" OR "fully remote" OR "work remotely")
```

### Remote OSINT Investigator Roles
```
site:linkedin.com ("OSINT investigator" OR "open source investigator") AND ("actively recruiting remotely" OR "join our remote team") AND ("remote" OR "telecommute")
```

### Remote Cyber Intelligence and OSINT
```
site:linkedin.com ("cyber intelligence analyst" OR "OSINT research") AND ("remote hiring" OR "remote opportunities") AND ("remote" OR "virtual")
```

### Remote OSINT Research Positions
```
